  "original_title": "DMT \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dcf\u0daf\u0dcf \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0dc3\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "DMT closes Friday",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Department of Motor Transport has decided to remain closed on Fridays due to the problematic situation that has arisen for its staff to report to work due to the current fuel supply restrictions in the country.",
        "The department has taken the decision according to the circular issued by the government in this regard. However, the department will be open on the 15th.",
        "After that, the department will be closed on Fridays, unless there is a public holiday that is not a Friday within the 5 working days of the week.",
        "For driving licenses - 070-7677977 can be obtained by calling on working days from 9.00 am to 4.00 pm."
      ],
